r you''re doing it perfectly.", "start": 181.26, "end": 188.54}, {"text": "Forgiving.", "start": 191.30501, "end": 191.945}, {"text": "It''s it''s more forgiving.", "start": 191.945, "end": 193.865}], "num_words": 50, "start": 162.45, "end": 193.865}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Right?", "start": 193.865, "end": 194.105}, {"text": "It''s it''s more forgiving.", "start": 194.105, "end": 195.38501}, {"text": "Right?", "start": 195.38501, "end": 195.945}, {"text": "Yeah.", "start": 198.505, "end": 198.825}, {"text": "So so so it is easier to start, but but it is also much easier to lose control over it.", "start": 198.825, "end": 208.33}], "num_words": 27, "start": 193.865, "end": 208.33}, {"sentences": [{"text": "And this is this is this is but, of course, you know, we should not exaggerate because because these accidents are not every day.", "start": 209.04999, "end": 220.945}, {"text": "I mean, it''s it''s happened especially if yeah.", "start": 220.945, "end": 226.225}, {"text": "It it it happens, but but especially if someone overestimate its ability.", "start": 226.225, "end": 235.4}, {"text": "Right?", "start": 235.4, "end": 236.04001}, {"text": "So so because there are some techniques that if you if you feel unstable, if you feel in danger, you can kill the power.", "start": 236.84, "end": 244.84}], "num_words": 69, "start": 209.04999, "end": 244.84}, {"sentences": [{"text": "And if if you if you try if you''re well trained and if you if you know these techniques, it''s pretty safe because because, you know, the the cats maybe you saw that the kite is connected with yourself with with something we call trappers.", "start": 245.40501, "end": 269.2}, {"text": "Is that I''m not whether this is also English, but yeah.", "start": 269.2, "end": 277.145}, {"text": "Yeah.", "start": 283.945, "end": 284.26498}, {"text": "Yeah.", "start": 284.92, "end": 285.40002}, {"text": "And also and also you have you have in your head, you have the bar steering bar.", "start": 285.4000